Key Match Events: Adil Faouzi opened the scoring for Morocco in the 18th minute
Azzedine Ounahi scored a stunning strike from outside the box in the 38th minute
Ounahi scored his second goal in the 45th minute
Soufiane Rahimi converted a penalty in the 71st minute
Post-Match Reflections: Under head coach Walid Regragui, the Atlas Lions aim to secure their third consecutive win
Regragui seeks to improve the national team’s overall performance
Miscellaneous Highlights: Yassine Bounou, Morocco’s goalkeeper, was substituted due to a hamstring strain
Others: The match was officiated by Gambian referee Bakary Gassama
